telling the truth.

180
00:06:17,690 --> 00:06:20,220
I can't tell you how much that
means to me, Harold, but...

181
00:06:20,230 --> 00:06:22,299
Mike, I want to
do this for you, please.

182
00:06:22,300 --> 00:06:23,799
I know you do.

183
