picture in the yearbook.

205
00:07:10,280 --> 00:07:11,579
Let's talk about
the yearbook.

206
00:07:11,580 --> 00:07:13,579
As he told you,
I'm not in the yearbook.

207
00:07:13,580 --> 00:07:14,740
Where is Mike Ross?

208
00:07:14,750 --> 00:07:16,280
Though what he didn't
tell you is that

209
00:07:16,290 --> 00:07:18,519
